name: Tule Canyon
description:
Introduction

A West Clear Creek Wilderness canyon.

Approach

Follow power lines road into canyon.

Descent

R1: 20' off of tree back from drop. Can be down climbed by the skilled.

R2: 50' off of tree back from drop.

R3: 40' off of tree RDC.

Exit

Follow WCC down until flattens out on left. Beautiful section of WCC with many nice pools. Follow ridge rib to the top on lightly used switch back trail. Follow power lines road back to vehicle.
